hu.elte.txtuml.api

Interface ModelValue

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ModelElement
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ModelBool, ModelBool.Else, ModelClass, ModelInt, ModelString, ModelType

    public interface ModelValue
extends ModelElement
    Base interface for classes and interfaces that might be used in the model as types of attributes or types of parameters and return values of constructors and operations.

    Represents: model objects or primitive values

    Usage:

    Should not be used directly.

    Java restrictions:

    • Define subtype: disallowed

    See the documentation of Model for an overview on modeling in txtUML.

    Author:
    Gabor Ferenc Kovacs
    See Also:
    ModelClass, ModelType
